	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello everybody.
<br />I cant seem to find any information about how to add a WRAM/SRAM to NROM cart. Are there any docs anywhere on how to do this? Im trying to make a Family Basic(V1) cardridge, but do not know how to decode 2kb ram(WE, OE, CE) and two prg_româ€™s only one 74HC20. 
<br />
<br /><img src="http://img136.imageshack.us/img136/1625/80919047wq4.png" alt="Image" />
<br />
<br /><img src="http://img222.imageshack.us/img222/7294/famrx5.jpg" alt="Image" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
